text: Þis is Peading tunes landscaro þær æscburne ut scyt.
On dertan <stream> od wede burne ut scyt.
Up an wede burnan oþ wiði mor, of widi more on cealfa dune.
Middewearde of cealfa dune <oð> sufonstanas.
Of sufonstanum on hyfan treow, on hyfan treowe on hord burh.
Of hordbyrg on deorford, of deorforda on langa stan.
Of langa stane on eofede tor, of eofede torre on hean dune forewearde.
Of heandune on þone blindan wille, of ðam wille on writelanstan.
Of þa stane on ruwa beorh, of ruwan beorge on fyrspenn.
Of fyrspenne on wyrtcumes heafod, of wyrtcumes heafde on rammes horn.
Of rammes horne on lulca stile, of lulca stile on wice cumes heafod.
On lymenstream oþ woggawill lacu utscyt, on þa lace oð wocgawilles hafod.
Of wocggawilles heafde on þone weg oð þa greatan dic oþ þere dic on þone wille on þæs mores heafod.
On þa lace to þære sweliende, of ðære sweliende on yederes beorh.
Of iederes beorge on standun <niðewearde> oþ þa gretan linde.
Of þære linde on dyra snæd middewearne.
Of dyra snæde on hwita ford, on hwita forda on fulanford.
Of fulanforda on hildes ford, of hildesforda on hildes lege norðewearde of sole get.
Of soleget to brynes cnolle suðeweardum on puneces wurði.
Of puneces wurþige on hremnes cumes heafod, of hremnes cumbe on þa riðe oð æscburnan.
Þanon on stream to dertan.
Pedingtunes land gemæro, bunde per dert.
